Roadmap
=======

Target
0.0.x       Improve room.updateTimes to eventually update older entries
            Admin option to clear room without deleting it
            User options
            * Separate flash and title visual alerts into two options
            * Provide custom e-mail address for alerts
            * Set alert time ranges
            * Colour picker
0.1.0       Initial release
0.2.0       Support for long-polling and websockets

The roadmap is subject to change; let me know if something is important to you.
